1
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:17,680
=Episode 23=
(The Mastermind)

3
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:30,460
(Number One)

4
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:38,180
(Staff badge)

5
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:02,879
Su Li,

6
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:03,959
I heard

7
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,159
someone filed a report
with the newspaper,

8
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:06,519
confirming the editor took bribes.

9
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:08,560
He's been fired.

10
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:09,840
I know.

11
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:10,919
Mu Shaoze did it.

12
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,080
I knew it.

13
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,599
Alright.

14
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:16,159
Now it's our turn to make a big move.

15
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:18,800
Oh no!

16
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,199
Meiyan is in trouble!

17
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,319
My face!

18
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:23,960
(Carcinogens Found in Meiyan Serum)

19
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:24,980
(Prohibited Ingredient TAF990
Exposed as Shocking Scandal)

20
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,039
Is my face also messed up?

21
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:26,879
Hello, everyone.

22
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,000
I am currently

23
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,360
at the Deep News office.

24
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,680
Their report on Meiyan cosmetics

25
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:33,680
containing harmful ingredients

26
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:34,879
has now been verified.

27
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,800
The company's person-in-charge,
He Jinchen,

28
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:37,919
is currently under investigation

29
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,759
and will soon face legal consequences.

30
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,840
He Jinchen took full responsibility

31
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,680
to protect the He family.

32
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,800
I have a feeling

33
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,680
this won't end so easily.

34
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:51,919
(Uncle Mu,)

35
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,280
(my father isn't here.)

36
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:54,560
(You can talk to me)

37
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:55,439
(about the raw material issue.)

38
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:58,479
(To cut costs and boost effectiveness,)

39
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:00,280
(you used raw materials)

40
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:02,319
(containing carcinogens
in the cosmetics.)

41
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,120
(Do you know you're harming people?)

42
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,319
(I will not stand by and do nothing.)

43
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:10,319
(Uncle Mu, don't worry,)

44
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:12,000
(we'll never use this ingredient again.)

45
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,960
(Please don't make this public.)

46
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:14,680
(Alright?)

47
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:16,680
(Jinchen,)

48
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,960
(I need to talk to him.)

49
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,240
It's He Mingyuan.

50
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:23,960
So,

51
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,000
the last person your father met

52
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,120
wasn't He Jinchen.

53
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,599
It was He Mingyuan.

54
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,400
No wonder He Jinchuan
wouldn't give you the recording.

55
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:37,039
He Mingyuan.

56
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:48,520
Enough, enough!

57
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,319
Stop it!

58
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:50,360
Are you okay?

59
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,080
Let me see.

60
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,039
Who sent them here?

61
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,599
Probably the He family.

62
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,639
I won't let them get away with this.

63
00:03:59,439 --> 00:03:59,879
Dad,

64
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,840
you always told me to stand for justice

65
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:05,319
and live with a clear conscience.

66
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:08,120
But justice couldn't keep you alive,

67
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:10,840
nor could it make our enemies pay.

68
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,400
Instead,

69
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,639
it keeps hurting the people I love.

70
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,079
So,

71
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:23,000
I will make them pay

72
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,519
in their way!

73
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,040
(Go to Plan B.)

74
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:37,720
Mu Shaoze.

75
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,639
What brings you here?

76
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:45,439
What is Plan B?

77
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,519
This

78
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,000
is none of your concern.

79
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:51,920
You don't need to be involved.

80
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,600
I'm telling you, I don't agree.

81
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:56,600
If we break the law to get revenge,

82
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,480
how are we any different from them?

83
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,519
It's been eight years.

84
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:03,959
I can't take it anymore.

85
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:08,079
I can't let He Mingyuan

86
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,199
hurt anyone I love ever again.

87
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,600
Especially you.

88
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:15,079
To me,

89
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:16,439
in this world,

90
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,360
you are the most important person.

91
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,399
I won't let anything happen to you.

92
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,319
You once asked me

93
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,480
where this scar came from.

94
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,879
I can tell you now.

95
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:30,759
I once went undercover
in a pyramid scheme.

96
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:33,399
I was stabbed by the ringleader.

97
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:36,360
I could have fought back
and taken him out,

98
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,680
but I held back.

99
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:40,680
I escaped with my life

100
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,680
and called the police.

101
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,800
Based on the ringleader's confession,

102
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:47,600
the police took down
the entire organization

103
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:49,680
and rescued hundreds of lives.

104
00:05:55,639 --> 00:05:56,360
Mu Shaoze,

105
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:59,240
you can't let hatred
consume your integrity.

106
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:07,680
You're right.

107
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:10,720
The guilty ones

108
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,480
aren't worth dirtying our hands over.

109
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:31,639
You...

110
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:32,920
What do you want?

111
00:06:33,759 --> 00:06:35,240
After how I treated you before,

112
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,759
you're not going to poison me, are you?

113
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,000
Mom,

114
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,040
it's just fever reducer.

115
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,759
It'll help you feel better.

116
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,920
I'm sorry for how I treated you before.

117
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:58,519
I know He Mingyuan

118
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,160
never stopped thinking
about your mother.

119
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:03,240
So I've been holding grudges inside

120
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,680
and taking it out on you.

121
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,319
Would you forgive me?

122
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,720
What he is,

123
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,439
we both know that now, don't we?

124
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,959
He'll sacrifice anyone

125
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,959
for his own gain and survival.

126
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,000
You're not Gu Qingmei.

127
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,439
Of course I'm Gu Qingmei.

128
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:26,319
And...

129
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,360
we'll get you out of here.

130
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,279
I've handled the guards outside.

131
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,439
We can leave now.

132
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:37,920
Take her and go first.

133
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:39,959
I have one more thing to do.

134
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:42,759
Alright.

135
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:51,560
You lose.

136
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,800
Xia Lan,

137
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,279
you have outplayed me again.

138
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,720
What use is skill at chess

139
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:03,000
when life is like a game?

140
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,319
We're all just pawns of fate.

141
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,279
We're helpless.

142
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,120
Fate?

143
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,959
I don't believe in fate.

144
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:13,600
I only believe in myself.

145
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:16,199
I'm the one in control.

146
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,279
So,

147
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:21,759
even your most favored son, He Jinchen,

148
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,879
is just a pawn to you.

149
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:25,519
Jinchen...

150
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,000
He is indecisive,

151
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,279
incapable of greatness.

152
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:31,040
He can only be a discarded piece.

153
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:36,080
You're quite the chameleon.

154
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,519
But that's fine.

155
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,720
Either way,

156
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:46,360
I've gathered enough material.

157
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:48,919
What are you doing?

158
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,399
You dare scheme against me?

159
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,799
This isn't scheming.

160
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:56,799
This

161
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,679
is a game of chess.

162
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:02,159
Isn't chess your favorite game?

163
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,440
What do you want?

164
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:13,879
If you don't want the world to know

165
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:16,120
who you really are,

166
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,039
sign this.

167
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:20,559
Return the resort

168
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,000
you stole from me.

169
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:28,360
Destroying it won't help you.

170
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,279
The video

171
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,480
is already uploaded to the cloud.

172
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:35,000
With one tap,

173
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:38,360
it goes out to countless media outlets.

174
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,080
Fine.

175
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,039
Gu Qingmei, I underestimated you.

176
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,919
You've got quite the cunning.

177
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,360
Why do you think I've become this way?

178
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,759
You all drove me to it.

179
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,559
Fine.

180
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,120
You got me.

181
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,200
I'll sign it.

182
00:10:06,340 --> 00:10:09,100
(He Mingyuan)

183
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:12,879
Here.

184
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,720
You're Xia Lan's daughter.

185
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:25,840
Why would you betray me too?

186
00:10:29,759 --> 00:10:30,240
He Mingyuan!

187
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,879
Let my sister go!

188
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:32,559
Fine.

189
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,000
Good.

190
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,399
You're all here.

191
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,519
Sisters sticking together.

192
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,320
Someone!

193
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,399
Get them now!

194
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:55,159
You hit me!

195
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,399
So what if I did?

196
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:59,240
When you locked me up and tortured me,

197
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,519
did you think about this day?

198
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,120
When you humiliated me
with your sick ways,

199
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,480
tortured me,

200
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,879
you should have seen

201
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,320
this karma coming.

202
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:13,360
Do you know why my mother
never liked you?

203
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,919
Because you're sick.

204
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:19,399
You're nothing but a parasite

205
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:22,399
who uses money and power
to control people.

206
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:24,600
You never deserved
my mother's affection.

207
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,440
No!

208
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,639
She looked down on me for being poor.

209
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,720
But I'm rich now!

210
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:31,440
I have everything!

211
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:33,120
She belongs to me!

212
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:34,879
Just you wait!

213
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,000
Just you wait!

214
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:51,120
Sis,

215
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:52,720
are you okay?

216
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:54,960
I'm fine.

217
00:11:58,679 --> 00:12:00,279
What you need is in this phone.

218
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,600
Take it.

219
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:39,000
(I don't believe in fate.)

220
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,519
(I only believe in myself.)

221
00:12:41,039 --> 00:12:43,240
(Even your most favored son,
He Jinchen,)

222
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:45,039
(is just a pawn to you.)

223
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,000
(Jinchen...)

224
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,559
(He is indecisive,
incapable of greatness.)

225
00:12:49,159 --> 00:12:50,440
(He can only be a discarded piece.)

226
00:12:53,039 --> 00:12:53,720
He Jinchen,

227
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:56,039
you thought you were
protecting the He family,

228
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,440
but you didn't know

229
00:12:58,159 --> 00:13:00,559
you were just a pawn
in your father's game.

230
00:13:01,039 --> 00:13:01,840
Stop it.

231
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:04,360
Your attempts to drive a wedge
won't work on me.

232
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,440
Don't you see it?

233
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:09,200
If you want to clear your name

234
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:11,200
and walk out with your head held high,

235
00:13:11,679 --> 00:13:13,279
you must confess everything

236
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:15,679
and let your father face justice.

237
00:13:17,399 --> 00:13:18,399
But he's my father.

238
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,559
If he falls,

239
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:21,200
the He family falls.

240
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:23,240
He already destroyed the He family.

241
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,799
He Jinchen, don't be a fool.

242
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:27,440
To throw your life away

243
00:13:27,799 --> 00:13:28,919
for someone like him,

244
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:30,279
it's not worth it.

245
00:14:08,060 --> 00:14:12,820
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

246
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:17,660
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

247
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:22,220
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

248
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:27,140
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

249
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:30,940
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

250
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:35,740
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

251
00:14:35,740 --> 00:14:38,580
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

252
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:41,260
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

253
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:47,180
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

254
00:14:47,580 --> 00:14:54,380
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

255
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:59,340
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

256
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:06,300
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

257
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:13,420
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

258
00:15:13,620 --> 00:15:18,100
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

259
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:21,460
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

260
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:28,380
♪Right as I confess my love♪
